124    "function gradV!(grad,q)\n",
125    "#   C = μ * J_2 * R_e^2   \n",
126    "    C = 1.7554962315534863e10\n",
127    "    x = q[1]\n",
128    "    y = q[2]\n",
129    "    z = q[3]\n",
130    "    r2 = x^2 + y^2 + z^2\n",
131    "    r = sqrt(r2)\n",
132    "    sinth = z/r\n",
133    "    aux1 = 1.5*C/(r*r2^2)\n",
134    "    aux2 = 5*sinth^2\n",
135    "    aux3 = aux1*(1 - aux2)\n",
136    "    grad[1] = aux3*x\n",
137    "    grad[2] = aux3*y\n",
138    "    grad[3] = aux1*(3-aux2)*z\n",
139    "    return nothing\n",
140    "end"

374    "function NbodyODE!(du,u,Gm,t)\n",
375    "     N = length(Gm)\n",
376    "     for k in 1:3\n",
377    "        for i in 1:N\n",
378    "            du[k,i,1] = 0\n",
379    "        end\n",
380    "     end\n",
381    "     @inbounds for i in 1:N\n",
382    "        xi = u[1,i,1]\n",
383    "        yi = u[2,i,1]\n",
384    "        zi = u[3,i,1]\n",
385    "        Gmi = Gm[i] \n",
386    "        for j in i+1:N\n",
387    "            xij = xi - u[1,j,1]\n",
388    "            yij = yi - u[2,j,1]\n",
389    "            zij = zi - u[3,j,1] \n",
390    "            Gmj = Gm[j] \n",
391    "            dotij = (xij*xij+yij*yij+zij*zij)\n",
392    "            auxij = 1/(sqrt(dotij)*dotij) \n",
393    "            Gmjauxij = Gmj*auxij\n",
394    "            du[1,i,2] -= Gmjauxij*xij\n",
395    "            du[2,i,2] -= Gmjauxij*yij\n",
396    "            du[3,i,2] -= Gmjauxij*zij  \n",
397    "            Gmiauxij = Gmi*auxij\n",
398    "            du[1,j,2] += Gmiauxij*xij\n",
399    "            du[2,j,2] += Gmiauxij*yij\n",
400    "            du[3,j,2] += Gmiauxij*zij\n",
401    "        end\n",
402    "     end \n",
403    "     @inbounds for i in 1:3, j in 1:N\n",
404    "        du[i,j,1] = u[i,j,2]\n",
405    "     end\n",
406    "    return nothing\n",
407    "end\n"
408   ]
